 design of tightly-coupled massive antenna arrays as\nopposed to the widely-adopted \"disconnected\" designs that disregard MC by\nputting faith in the half-wavelength spacing rule.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 2 Aug 2022 16:03:12 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 6 May 2023 15:37:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-09"}
