ally spreading gamma-ray\nburst ejecta. The subsequent rebrightening, when these ejecta break through and\nshocks form, is very mild (${\\lesssim}10\\%$), and may not be observable.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 2 Aug 2022 16:03:48 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 13 Jan 2023 08:55:48 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-02-01"}
