mber of quantization bits does not influence the secrecy when exceeding\n$3$ bits. All the analytical results are endorsed by Monte Carlo simulations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 2 Aug 2022 20:24:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-08-04"}
