 Hungarian\nmethod is invoked to solve the outer problem. Numerical results demonstrate\nthat our proposed approach achieves lowest AoI compared to the other baseline\napproaches.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 2 Aug 2022 20:57:38 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 1 Sep 2022 22:54:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-09-05"}
