 the metal oxide precursor (which\ncontracts).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 3 Aug 2022 13:08:31 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 7 Dec 2022 02:38:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-12-08"}
